---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components"
---

<section id="como-funciona" class="py-24 bg-surface relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[400px] bg-red-500/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-white/5 text-gray-400 text-sm font-mono rounded-full mb-4">
                Metodologia Técnica
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
                Como resgatamos seu site
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                Não é chute. É análise técnica, plano de ação e execução cirúrgica
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="bg-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full hover:border-red-500/50 transition-colors text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-2xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20">
                            1
                        </div>
                        <Icon name="lucide:stethoscope" class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-500 mx-auto mb-4" />
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Diagnóstico</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Rodamos softwares de auditoria para identificar gargalos de servidor, código e imagens
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:mt-8">
                    <div class="bg-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full hover:border-red-500/50 transition-colors text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-2xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20">
                            2
                        </div>
                        <Icon name="lucide:file-code" class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-500 mx-auto mb-4" />
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Plano & Execução</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Definimos se é caso de ajuste (Lite), otimização pesada (Standard) ou reconstrução (Rebuild)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:mt-16">
                    <div class="bg-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full hover:border-red-500/50 transition-colors text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-2xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20">
                            3
                        </div>
                        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle-2" class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-500 mx-auto mb-4" />
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Estabilidade</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Entregamos o site limpo, rápido e com backup de segurança configurado
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 p-6 bg-red-900/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-2xl text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <Icon name="lucide:alert-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" />
                <p class="text-sm text-red-200">
                    Não trabalhamos com "gambiarra". Se o site não tiver salvação técnica, seremos honestos sobre o Rebuild.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
